Library: com.hyperxtalk.library.animationengine

Type: library

Title: AnimationEngine

Version: 2.9

Author: derbrill Multimedia

Description:
AnimationEngine is a LiveCode library for 2D and 3D animation. It provides
handlers for moving controls on linear, circular, elliptical and polygonal
paths, custom properties for constraining drag to rectangles, circles,
ellipses and lines, easing functions, collision detection, isometric and
perspective 3D coordinate conversion, and geometry utility functions.

Tags: animation, motion, geometry, collision, easing, isometric, 3d


Name: aeChangeTextSize

Type: command

Syntax: aeChangeTextSize pValue

Summary: Use this handler to change the textsize in a field, keeping the formatting intact. If you have a field with different styles and textSizes t

