Example: send aeChangeTextSize "-1" to field "myField"

Description:
Use this handler to change the textsize in a field, keeping the formatting intact. If you have a field with different styles and textSizes the handler grows or shrinks the textsizes relatively, keeping all styling intact. If the smallest size in the field has been reached, the result contains:

"Smallest size reached"



