Aboutthisdocument

Welcome to the animationEngine documentation.

How to use this stack:

Choose the name of a function, handler or property from the field on the right side. The document is divided into two parts, dictionary and examples. Every entry in the field on the right side that is displayed in blue, has an example. If the text is displayed in gray there is no example for that entry. You can switch between example and dictionary by clicking the appropriate button on top of this stack. The stack is searchable. You can choose if functions, handlers and properties should be displayed.

The documentation stack is self contained. You do not need to put animationEngine in use to watch the examples.

